OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with long
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. Feeling warm,
OL,7,Fespecially in the east, but cooler
OL,8,Falong the Solway Coast with patchy low
OL,9,Fcloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness then remaining
OL,13,Fdry overnight with clear spells. A
OL,14,Fvery mild night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FThe odd spot of rain is
OL,17,Fpossible early morning, otherwise dry
OL,18,Fwith plenty of sunshine and feeling
OL,19,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
